modules.description: This module implements a mutable trie structure where paths are lists of hashable elements. It supports creating trie nodes, associating values with paths, retrieving and removing values by path, and navigating to sub-nodes. Concrete use cases include efficient prefix-based lookups for auto-completion systems and hierarchical data storage with shared prefixes.
